## Artifact Management

Compiled Maven artifacts are automatically versioned and published to Nexus Repository Manager.

### Benefits

* Version Tracking
* Artifact Storage
* Build Reproducibility
* Dependency Management

![Nexus Repository](screenshots/nexus.png)

