## Running the Project

### Clone Repository

```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/event-management-devops.git
cd event-management-devops
```

### Start the Platform

```bash
docker-compose up -d
```

### Access Services

| Service     | URL                                                |
| ----------- | -------------------------------------------------- |
| Application | http://localhost:8089                              |
| Swagger UI  | http://localhost:8089/events/swagger-ui/index.html |
| Jenkins     | http://localhost:8080                              |
| SonarQube   | http://localhost:9000                              |
| Nexus       | http://localhost:8081                              |
| Prometheus  | http://localhost:9090                              |
| Grafana     | http://localhost:3000                              |

